data.description: This beautiful home located in Stateside welcomes its new owners! As you enter the home, the foyer leads you to the family room that features vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace. The kitchen has all stainless steel appliances with white cabinetry and granite countertops. Enjoy a formal dining space, perfect for entertaining. The master bedroom has a large walk in closet and an en suite equipped with a walk in shower, a large garden tub, and dual vanity sinks. This home is conveniently located only minutes from shopping and a short commute from Camp Lejeune. Schedule your showing today, this home won't last long!! Offering $500 Buyer Credit with acceptable offer until 11/20
